name: Abyss Actor - Superstar
desc:
Pendulum Effect
Once per turn: You can Tribute 1 "Abyss Actor" monster, then target 1 "Abyss Script" Spell in your GY; add it to your hand.

Monster Effect
When Normal or Special Summoned, your opponent's Spell/Traps and effects cannot be activated. Once per turn: You can Set 1 "Abyss Script" Spell directly from your Deck, but it is sent to the GY during the End Phase.
